      <p class="mb-8">
        We have unparalleled access to start-ups in India, built over two
        decades of on the ground presence and leadership in the AI ecosystem.
        The founding team has 125+ years of experience in underwriting
        technology and mentoring businesses globally. We have previously
        co-founded, incubated, and invested in 15+ AI and robotics companies.

