      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 header-color">
        India: a unique AI opportunity
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-8">
        Despite global economic uncertainties, India's growth outlook remains
        robust, building on a decade of stellar performance. This growth is
        fueled by strong domestic consumption, structural reforms, and a vibrant
        services sector. India offers significant opportunity and continues to
        attract foreign investment because of its young workforce, expanding
        digital infrastructure, and the government's focus on development and
        ease of doing business.

        <!-- Despite global economic uncertainties, India's growth outlook remains
